  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542550/extras/f7b1d272afdbcad6a9e41be248af77f8.apng?t=1737986670\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542550/extras/f7b1d272afdbcad6a9e41be248af77f8.poster.avif?t=1737986670\" class=\"bb_img\" width=624 height=192 /></picture></span><br><br>Help this charismatic mole collect matchsticks in a haunted mine in this challenging platform game!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Easy-to-learn gameplay and tight controls.<br><br></li><li> Beautiful graphics in pixel art that refer to the most nostalgic games of the 8bit era.<br><br></li><li> An optional retro filter that will increase the nostalgia even more.<br><br></li><li> The best of chiptune in an immersive and memorable soundtrack.<br><br></li><li> Play 40 levels including boss battles.<br><br></li><li> Cute characters and enemies.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542550/extras/b1270bc88434865cfb81a383f481e1ef.apng?t=1737986670\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542550/extras/b1270bc88434865cfb81a383f481e1ef.poster.avif?t=1737986670\" class=\"bb_img\" width=624 height=192 /></picture></span><br><br>You're not going to let this adorable mole get cold, are you?",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542550/extras/f7b1d272afdbcad6a9e41be248af77f8.apng?t=1737986670\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542550/extras/f7b1d272afdbcad6a9e41be248af77f8.poster.avif?t=1737986670\" class=\"bb_img\" width=624 height=192 /></picture></span><br><br>Help this charismatic mole collect matchsticks in a haunted mine in this challenging platform game!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Easy-to-learn gameplay and tight controls.<br><br></li><li> Beautiful graphics in pixel art that refer to the most nostalgic games of the 8bit era.<br><br></li><li> An optional retro filter that will increase the nostalgia even more.<br><br></li><li> The best of chiptune in an immersive and memorable soundtrack.<br><br></li><li> Play 40 levels including boss battles.<br><br></li><li> Cute characters and enemies.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542550/extras/b1270bc88434865cfb81a383f481e1ef.apng?t=1737986670\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542550/extras/b1270bc88434865cfb81a383f481e1ef.poster.avif?t=1737986670\" class=\"bb_img\" width=624 height=192 /></picture></span><br><br>You're not going to let this adorable mole get cold, are you?",
